headline: Keurig Dr Pepper gains amid Starboard Value reportedly taking stake
summary: Investing.com -- Shares of Keurig Dr Pepper are trading roughly 2.5% higher in a volume spike midday on Monday, after a report by The Financial Times suggesting activist investor Starboard Value has taken a stake in the company.
